des:
Listen to this interactive story about a little boy who wants to be a justice league cop!. A must have for your bag of stories, this story inspires bravery, inspired by the Indian Franchise Singham, a story of a justice league cop. Listen on to how he saves a little girl's life from a sinkhole by grabbing her from her shoulder arm.
 At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
